    <item>
      <title>花旗集团和阿波罗联手推出 250 亿美元私人信贷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/citigroup-apollo-join-forces-in-25-billion-private-credit-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团和阿波罗全球管理公司正在快速增长的私人信贷市场展开联手，同意在未来五年内共同完成价值 250 亿美元的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/citigroup-apollo-join-forces-in-25-billion-private-credit-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通纳入印度市场刺激债务需求，印度维持借贷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/india-maintains-borrowing-as-jpm-inclusion-fuels-debt-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在全球债务纳入刺激大量外资流入的背景下，印度政府维持了本财年剩余时间的借贷计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/india-maintains-borrowing-as-jpm-inclusion-fuels-debt-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 12:17:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Eskom 涨价请求有望带来债券收益和客户压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/eskom-price-hike-request-promises-bond-gains-and-customer-strain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国家电力公司 (Eskom Holdings SOC Ltd.) 正在寻求大幅提高电价，这对其债权人来说是个好消息，但会给消费者带来痛苦，并可能对该国的经济增长造成影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/eskom-price-hike-request-promises-bond-gains-and-customer-strain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 12:02:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰亿万富翁家族纠纷导致 Cyfrowy 股价创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/polish-billionaire-family-s-dispute-stokes-record-cyfrowy-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份报告披露了波兰亿万富翁创始人家族为争夺这家波兰媒体、能源和电信集团的控制权而产生的内讧，此后，Cyfrowy Polsat SA 的股价有望创下有史以来最大单日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/polish-billionaire-family-s-dispute-stokes-record-cyfrowy-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 11:57:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
