      <title>贵金属价格上涨，白银价格飙升至 2012 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/silver-surges-to-the-highest-since-2012-as-precious-metals-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储进一步降息的预期提振了贵金属价格，白银价格触及2012年以来的最高水平，黄金价格也创下新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/silver-surges-to-the-highest-since-2012-as-precious-metals-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 11:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国誓言支持经济增长，铜价再次突破 10,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/base-metals-edge-lower-as-doubts-swirl-over-china-s-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国高层领导人加大刺激经济增长力度的带动下，铜价自 7 月份以来首次回升至每吨 10,000 美元，其他工业金属价格也出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/base-metals-edge-lower-as-doubts-swirl-over-china-s-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:30:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特和利比亚有望增加石油供应，油价继续大幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-26</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，沙特阿拉伯承诺在 12 月份增加产量，而利比亚各派达成协议，可能为恢复部分原油生产铺平道路，导致油价连续第二天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-26</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:30:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最新数据公布后，美国股指期货继续走高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国承诺实施财政刺激措施以及交易员对各大央行降息预期增加的预期推动，全球股市出现上涨。美国最新经济数据也提振了市场人气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 22:41:13 GMT</pubDate>
